            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Preview -->
    <section class="section about-preview">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>Who We Are</h2>
                <p>Excellence in minimalist architecture and design</p>
            </div>
            <div class="about-content">
                <div class="about-text">
                    <h3>Minimalist Architecture Studio</h3>
                    <p>Minimalist Architecture is a leading design studio dedicated to creating innovative, sustainable, and minimalist architectural spaces. Our team of talented architects and designers bring together decades of experience to transform visions into elegant reality.</p>
